          <h1><a href="how-curbee-helps-dealers-launch-and-grow-mobile-service.html">More Than Tech: How Curbee Helps Dealers Launch & Grow Mobile Service</a></h1>
        </div>
        <div class="info">
          <span> Written by <a class="author-link" href="author/curbee%3FhsLang=en.html">Curbee</a> | July 22, 2025 </span>
        </div>
        <div class="blog-section">
          <span><p><span><span><strong>Amit Chandarana - CEO<br>Chris Buller - Sr. Director, Dealer Success<br><br></strong></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><strong>Big Market. Bigger Opportunity. And We're Leading It.&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>

<p>Adding mobile service shouldn’t mean tearing your whole operation apart. But it does take more than throwing tools in a van and handing your best tech an iPad.</p>
<p>At Curbee, we’re not just a plug-and-play SaaS platform. We’re your real-world partner for building, launching, and growing a mobile service program that works for your customers and your team. From helping you map out career paths for your technicians to making sure your tarps don’t stain a customer’s driveway, we unpack the details you haven't thought about yet.</p>
<p>And here’s the kicker: adding mobile service with Curbee is a smart, super <strong>efficient capital expenditure</strong>. Instead of spending $200,000+ to build a new bay and disrupt your <span><span><span>entire</span></span> shop—if you have the real estate—you can get mobile service rolling in under 30 days, </span>under $20K with our <a href="https://vimeo.com/1093247162?share=copy" rel="noopener">software, solutions, and support</a>.</p>
<p>Our technology makes booking mobile appointments easy and intuitive. It’s guided for your advisors, clear for your customers, and seamless for your techs. But that’s just the start.</p>
<h4>What's Driving Consumer Demand?</h4>
<p>No two stores are the same. Some need to <a href="https://youtu.be/ONN3D0iWKx0?feature=shared" rel="noopener">retrofit</a> a $12,000 crossover to get started. Others roll out a fully loaded OEM van but still need the practical touches to make it work.</p>
<p>That’s where we come in. We meet you where you are, just like you meet your customers where they are.&nbsp;</p>
<p>Like:</p>
<ul>
<li>A mobile eye wash station (trust us, even the big fancy vans forget this)</li>
<li>Smart storage for nitrile gloves, damp rags, wipes, and tarps</li>
<li>A two-color tarp system so the clean side always protects your customer’s driveway</li>
<li>Handy extras like portable hand-washing kits</li>
<li>And don’t forget the dog treats – IYKYK</li>
</ul>
<p>We’ve supported over 30,000 mobile service visits and dozens of dealer programs, so we know exactly which real-world details make all the difference.</p>
<h4>It's Not Just Tech. It's Not Just a Van. It's Change Management.</h4>
<p>Success with mobile isn’t just about the van. It’s about your people and how you adapt.</p>
<p>That’s why our team helps you rethink the soft side of mobile:<br><em>How does mobile affect your spiff program? If your advisor earns 5 percent, how do they get paid when the job’s in a driveway instead of a bay?</em></p>
<p>Curbee helps dealers launch new technician career development pathways and pay structures so techs see mobile as growth, not just extra or lower-paid work.</p>
<p>We help you see the full picture—the vehicle, the tools, the people, and the smart operational shifts that keep your mobile service profitable, sustainable, and built for happy customers who come back for more.</p>
<blockquote>
<p><em>“<a href="https://vimeo.com/1088484860?share=copy" rel="noopener">Working with Curbee is night and day easier than doing it yourself</a>,” said Ron Scott, Service Manager at Kelley Buick GMC. “If I had any advice for someone thinking about mobile service? Do it.”</em></p>
</blockquote>
<h4>Launch Kits and Human Help&nbsp;</h4>
<p>From QR codes for easy scheduling to same-day ride-alongs, our Success Managers are in the trenches with you. Literally.</p>
<blockquote>
<p><em>“<a href="https://vimeo.com/1088484860?share=copy" rel="noopener">Chris rode with me for a day</a>. That was the first time I’d ever had a company rep go out into the wild with me,” said Ryan Yoder, mobile tech at Kelley Buick GMC.</em></p>
</blockquote>
<p>But we don’t stop at setup.</p>
<p>We equip you with proven best practices and toolkits to launch and grow your mobile service business. From examples to marketing playbooks, we help guide you to double appointments in your first six months.</p>
<p>Whether it’s how to position mobile service or where to promote it, we guide your go-to-market efforts to drive real results.</p>
<p>At Curbee, we don’t just send training videos and software and walk away. We ride along. We’re there and happy to come back until your mobile service is running smoothly and profitably. We’re in it for the long haul.</p>
<p>And it pays off. Dealers who run mobile with Curbee don’t just expand capacity. They make more money by creating more satisfied customers.</p>
<h4>Flexible Tech, Tailored for You</h4>
<p>Our software is intuitive, guided, and purpose-built for simple mobile service. But what really sets Curbee apart is how quickly we adapt it to your operation, so you don’t have to force your store into a one-size-fits-all box.</p>
<blockquote>
<p><em>“I have to say, and I’m not blowing smoke, this launch with Curbee has been the best launch of any software company I have experienced,” said Ryan Sokoloff, Partner and Fixed Ops Director at Susquehanna Automotive, a Chrysler, Dodge, Jeep, Ram dealer in Pennsylvania. “What made this so special was the level of knowledge Curbee brought and their ability to make software adjustments tailored to our business so quickly. I really appreciate the two days our Curbee Success Manager spent with us.”</em></p>
</blockquote>
<h4>Your Partner, From First Mile to Forever</h4>
<p>At Curbee, we know that what sounds simple—add mobile service—actually runs deep: people, process, pay, trust, and change.</p>
<p>So when we say we’re more than just technology, we mean it.</p>
<p>We help you <span>plan it.</span><br>We help you <span>build it</span>.<br>We help you <span>launch it</span>.<br>We help you <span>grow it</span>.</p>
<p>This is why we’re the largest mobile service provider to dealers, and why we’re growing fast.</p>
